==English==
====Etymology====
From Greek [[όπλον]] (arms, armor, weapon) and [[φόβος]] (fear, fright, terror). Cf. [[hoplite]].

===Pronunciation===
(HAWP.luh.FOH.bee.uh) 

===Noun===
'''hoplophobia'''

# ''(often used derogatorily)'' The fear of guns.

